Class EndpointWebMvcChildContextConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.boot.actuate.autoconfigure.EndpointWebMvcChildContextConfiguration

  • @Configuration
 @EnableWebMvc
 @Import(value=org.springframework.boot.actuate.autoconfigure.ManagementContextConfigurationsImportSelector.class)
public class EndpointWebMvcChildContextConfiguration
extends Object
    Configuration triggered from EndpointWebMvcAutoConfiguration when a new EmbeddedServletContainer running on a different port is required.
